column2: "Partner! Keep out of this, ok? This is just between siblings."

"Sibling? a Dark Falz... sibling!
Hah, don't make me laugh!"
"I bet it is funny... But it's the truth, so you'll need to deal with it!"
"Shut up... I don't have any siblings!"

"Whether or not that you believe
we're siblings doesn't matter!
If you have forgotten, then I'll
have to live with that!"
"I just want you to return to being yourself, Yuki-nee!"
"You... How about you! Me, a Dark Falz, can you even try?"
"Why do both of you... have the same expression..."
"I am a Dark Falz... Am I not allowed to die?"
